location: Roadway shutdown at New Circle Rd until further notice due to an overturned semi past New Circle Rd.
Outbound traffic diverted to the inner loop of New Circle Rd toward Old Frankfort Pike.
The exit ramps from New Circle Rd to outbound Versailles Rd also shutdown.
Inbound Versailles Rd is down to one lane at the scene.
Inbound Nicholasville Rd between Tahoma Rd and Shady Ln
